OL,3,CFormer Daily Mail journalist
OL,4,C'completely devastated' by Doreen
OL,5,CLawrence claims
OL,7,FThe Daily Mail's former crime editor
OL,8,Fhas said he was "completely
OL,9,Fdevastated" by allegations of unlawful
OL,10,Finformation gathering made by Baroness
OL,11,FDoreen Lawrence against him, the High
OL,12,FCourt has heard.
OL,14,FStephen Wright, who worked for the
OL,15,Fnewspaper for 33 years, was the latest
OL,16,Fperson to give evidence in the High
OL,17,FCourt trial of claims brought by a
OL,18,Fgroup of household names against
OL,19,FAssociated Newspapers Limited (ANL).
