OL,3,CFormer Daily Mail journalist
OL,4,C'completely devastated' by Doreen
OL,5,CLawrence claims
OL,7,FThe journalist has a byline on the
OL,8,Ffive articles in Lady Lawrence's
OL,9,Fclaim, which were published between
OL,10,F1997 and 2007.
OL,12,FIn her claim, the peer alleges ANL had
OL,13,Ftargeted her with hidden electronic
OL,14,Fsurveillance, as well as tapping her
OL,15,Flandline, monitoring her bank account
OL,16,Fand making payments to police officers
OL,17,Ffor confidential information.
OL,19,FANL has strongly denied wrongdoing and
OL,20,Fhas previously described the claims as
OL,21,Fpreposterous.
