OL,7,FThey are defending the claims, which
OL,8,Fhave also been brought by high-profile
OL,9,Findividuals including the Duke of
OL,10,FSussex and Sir Elton John.
OL,12,FMr Wright began giving evidence on
OL,13,FTuesday, with the court in London told
OL,14,Fthat he had "lived under a cloud"
OL,15,Fsince the legal action was filed.
OL,17,FIn his witness statement, Mr Wright
OL,18,Fsaid: "It is no exaggeration to say
OL,19,Fthat when I first learned of Lady
OL,20,FLawrence's allegations against me, I
OL,21,Fwas completely devastated.
