OL,7,FThe Daily Mail campaigned to bring the
OL,8,Fkillers of Lady Lawrence's son Stephen
OL,9,Fto justice after his death in 1993.
OL,11,FOn the front page of the February 14
OL,12,Fedition in 1997, the paper labelled
OL,13,Ffive men ` Gary Dobson, Neil Acourt,
OL,14,FJamie Acourt, Luke Knight, and David
OL,15,FNorris ` as "murderers" and challenged
OL,16,Fthem to sue the newspaper for libel.
