OL,4,C'completely devastated' by Doreen
OL,5,CLawrence claims
OL,7,FShe said she felt "played for such a
OL,8,Flong time", adding: "To find out now
OL,9,Fthat after all that time, the level of
OL,10,Ftrust that I had built up, to find
OL,11,Fthat all that time he's been lying to
OL,12,Fme and pretending that he was
OL,13,Fsupporting my case and supporting
OL,14,Fgetting justice for Stephen."
OL,16,FIn his witness statement, Mr Wright
OL,17,Fsaid he was "shocked" by how he was
OL,18,Fdescribed by Lady Lawrence in legal
OL,19,Fdocuments.
